### Variables
@gatewayUrl = http://localhost:8080
@inventoryUrl = http://localhost:8082
@authUrl = http://localhost:8083
@orderUrl = http://localhost:8085

### ===================================================
### AUTH SERVICE
### ===================================================

### Login como admin → copiá el token en @token
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Login como user
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "user123"
}

###

### ===================================================
### INVENTORY SERVICE — vía API Gateway (con JWT)
### ===================================================

@token = Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbiIsInJvbGVzIjpbIlJPTEVfQURNSU4iLCJST0xFX1VTRVIiXSwiaWF0IjoxNzgwODY5MzgwLCJleHAiOjE3ODA4NzI5ODB9.yDMRDYZijjtk50sLM2sBS2XcKnuI9riRvA3Rn2reCGqgvX4TBAZgsW-8QQ0e6ntl

### Obtener todos los productos
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/inventory/products
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener todos los productos
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener producto por ID
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/inventory/products/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Crear producto
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/api/inventory/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "name": "Producto Test 2",
  "quantity": 10,
  "price": 99.99
}

###

### Crear orden
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "product": "Producto Test 2",
  "quantity": 7,
  "customer": "admin",
  "status": "PENDING"
}

###
### ===================================================
### INVENTORY SERVICE — acceso directo (sin gateway)
### ===================================================

### Obtener todos los productos (directo)
GET {{inventoryUrl}}/api/inventory/products
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener producto por ID (directo)
GET {{inventoryUrl}}/api/inventory/products/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Crear producto (directo)
POST {{inventoryUrl}}/api/inventory/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "name": "Producto Directo",
  "quantity": 5,
  "price": 49.99
}

###

### ===================================================
### ORDER SERVICE — vía API Gateway (con JWT)
### ===================================================

### Sin token → debe responder 401
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/orders

###

### Obtener todas las órdenes
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener orden por ID
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/orders/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Crear orden → publica OrderCreated (lo consume notification-service)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "product": "Monitor",
  "quantity": 2,
  "customer": "admin",
  "status": "CREATED"
}

###

### ===================================================
### HEALTH CHECKS
### ===================================================

### Eureka
GET http://localhost:8761/actuator/health

###

### Config Server
GET http://localhost:8888/actuator/health

###

### Inventory Service
GET {{inventoryUrl}}/actuator/health

###

### H2 Console (inventory-service)
### Abrí en el browser: http://localhost:8082/h2-console
